The mail system has been revised.

You may now send Cc:'s to multiple destinations:

Either by separating with a space or by separating with a comma.

e.g. Cc: moonchild james
or:  Cc: moonchild, james
or:  Cc: moonchild,james

You now have a limit on the number of mails you can store at once.
